### Footnotes

<span id="fn_341"></span>[99:1](sbe2251.htm#fr_347.md) In honour of the
gods.

<span id="fn_342"></span>[100:1](sbe2251.htm#fr_348.md) This stands for
uvvale*gg*a vâ uvva*tt*e*gg*â vâ (udvaled vâ udvarted vâ), for which
words, denoting some rather indistinct varieties of rubbing, I know no
adequate English words.

<span id="fn_343"></span>[100:2](sbe2251.htm#fr_349.md) The words in
