<span id="fn_344"></span>[101:1](sbe2251.htm#fr_350.md) This might also be
translated: at an opposite door.

<span id="fn_345"></span>[101:2](sbe2251.htm#fr_351.md) The following
passage is not explained in the commentaries, and is wanting in the
